{"id":1396,"type":"vertex","label":"hoverResult","result":{"contents":{"kind":"markdown","value":"\n```rust\nrust_sample\n```\n\n```rust\nconst USAGE: &str = \"\ntodos.\nUsage:\n  todos new <name>\n  todos list [--lf=<lfsp>] [--status=<s>]\n  todos edit <index>\n  todos status <index> <stat>\n  todos rm <index>\n  todos report [--type=<t>]\n  todos (-h | --help)\n  todos --version\nOptions:\n  -h --help    \tShow this screen.\n  --version     Show version.\n  --lf=<lfsp>   define lifespan (daily, weekly, monthly, yearly).\n  --type=<t>    report type (html, markdown).\n\"\n```"}}}
