{"id":2005,"type":"vertex","label":"hoverResult","result":{"contents":{"kind":"markdown","value":"\n```rust\nalloc::string::String\n```\n\n```rust\npub fn is_empty(&self) -> bool\n```\n\n---\n\nReturns `true` if this `String` has a length of zero, and `false` otherwise.\n\n# Examples\n\nBasic usage:\n\n```rust\nlet mut v = String::new();\nassert!(v.is_empty());\n\nv.push('a');\nassert!(!v.is_empty());\n```"}}}
