{"id":2605,"type":"vertex","label":"hoverResult","result":{"contents":{"kind":"markdown","value":"\n```rust\ncore::result::Result\n```\n\n```rust\npub fn unwrap_or_else<F>(self, op: F) -> T\nwhere\n    F: FnOnce(E) -> T,\n```\n\n---\n\nReturns the contained [`Ok`](https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/core/result/enum.Result.html) value or computes it from a closure.\n\n# Examples\n\nBasic usage:\n\n```rust\nfn count(x: &str) -> usize { x.len() }\n\nassert_eq!(Ok(2).unwrap_or_else(count), 2);\nassert_eq!(Err(\"foo\").unwrap_or_else(count), 3);\n```"}}}
