{"id":2804,"type":"vertex","label":"hoverResult","result":{"contents":{"kind":"markdown","value":"\n```rust\ncore::result::Result\n```\n\n```rust\npub fn ok(self) -> Option<T>\n```\n\n---\n\nConverts from `Result<T, E>` to [`Option<T>`](https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/core/option/enum.Option.html).\n\nConverts `self` into an [`Option<T>`](https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/core/option/enum.Option.html), consuming `self`,\nand discarding the error, if any.\n\n# Examples\n\nBasic usage:\n\n```rust\nlet x: Result<u32, &str> = Ok(2);\nassert_eq!(x.ok(), Some(2));\n\nlet x: Result<u32, &str> = Err(\"Nothing here\");\nassert_eq!(x.ok(), None);\n```"}}}
